餐廳常用英語會話

1.

what do you feel like?

（ 你想吃什麼？）

2.

What are you in the mood for? ( 你想吃什麼？)

3.

if you like________, you might want to try_____.(你喜歡＿＿，你可以試試＿＿這家店)

4.

I’m sorry. We don’t open until_____. We’re just getting set upnow. (對不起，我們＿＿才營業，現在還在準備中)

5.

we closed at______. (我們＿＿關門)

6.

we’ll let you know as soon as a table is available.(有空位時，我們會馬上通知你)

7.

there’s a ____ wait. Is that ok? (要等＿＿，這樣可以嗎？)

8.

how many in your party? (你們有幾位？)

9.

we’re full at the moment. Would you like to wait?(我們現在客滿了，你願意等嗎？)

10.

I’ll be with you in just a minute. (我馬上回來)

11.

sorry to keep you waiting. (抱歉讓你久等了)

12.

are you ready to order? (你可以點餐了嗎？)

13.

let me know when you’re ready to order? (決定好了再叫我)

14.

what would you like? (你想吃什麼？)

15.

a lot of people like the_____. (很多人喜歡＿＿)

16.

our______ is pretty good. (我們的＿＿很好吃)

17.

we’re pretty famous for our_____. (我們的＿＿很有名)

18.

would you like a refill? (你要續杯嗎？)

19.

let me repeat your order…. (讓我重複一次你點的餐．．．)

20.

I’m sorry. We don’t have take-out. (很抱歉，我們沒有外帶)

21.

right this way. (就在這邊)

22.

just follow me. (跟我來)

23.

the restroom is in back of the shop on your left.(洗手間就在商店後面，在你的左邊)

24.

may I take your plate? (我可以收走你的盤子嗎？)

25.

let me get that out of your way. (我幫你把桌子清乾淨)

26.

you can take the meal to the cashier.(你可以把餐拿到收銀)

27.

is this all on one check? (全部一起算嗎？)

28.

will this be cash or credit card? (付現金還是信用卡？)

29.

ok. Your total comes to____. (好的，總共是＿＿)

30.

thank you. Please come back and see us again.

1






































